    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1919-01-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1919-01-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="345"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d345">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">Robert Lansing Papers</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        French Ambassador to the United States</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Jusserand</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-01-13">13 January,
                            1919</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Mr. Ambassador</hi>: With reference to your letter
                    dated January 4th,<note n="26" xml:id="d345fn26">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_404">p. 404</ref>.</note>
                    regarding the question of making representations in connection with the
                    publication of a decree of the Roumanian Government uniting Transylvania and
                    Banat to Roumania, I take pleasure in informing you that the matter has been
                    referred to the American Embassy here for appropriate action.</p>
                <p>I am [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Robert Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
